M|Over|tx|LLMs respond to the same persuasion principles as humans. Understanding this ps helps you ds more effective skills - not to manipulate, but to ensure ct practices are followed even under pressure.
M|Over|**Re|** Meincke et al. (2025) tested 7 persuasion principles w/ N=28,000 AI conversations. Persuasion techniques more than doubled compliance rates (33% → 72%, p < .001).
